<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Privacy Policy - Anonymous Support</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/legal.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="legal-container">
      <div class="legal-content">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p class="last-updated">Last updated: March 6, 2024</p>

        <section>
          <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
          <h3>1.1 Account Information</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Email address (encrypted)</li>
            <li>Username (anonymous identifier)</li>
            <li>Password (encrypted)</li>
          </ul>

          <h3>1.2 Usage Data</h3>
          <ul>
            <li>Login timestamps</li>
            <li>Chat session durations</li>
            <li>Anonymous usage statistics</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p>We use your information to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Provide and maintain our anonymous support service</li>
            <li>Enable secure chat connections</li>
            <li>Improve user experience</li>
            <li>Ensure platform security</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>3. Data Protection</h2>
          <p>We implement strong security measures including:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>End-to-end encryption for messages</li>
            <li>Secure data storage using industry standards</li>
            <li>Regular security audits</li>
            <li>Automated threat detection</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>4. Your Privacy Rights</h2>
          <p>You have the right to:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Access your personal data</li>
            <li>Request data deletion</li>
            <li>Opt-out of non-essential data collection</li>
            <li>Receive a copy of your data</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>5. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>We retain your data as follows:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Account information: Until account deletion</li>
            <li>Chat messages: Not stored after delivery</li>
            <li>Usage logs: 30 days</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>6. Third-Party Services</h2>
          <p>We may use third-party services for:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Analytics (anonymized data only)</li>
            <li>Infrastructure and hosting</li>
            <li>Security monitoring</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>7. Cookies Policy</h2>
          <p>We use essential cookies for:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Session management</li>
            <li>Security purposes</li>
            <li>User preferences</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>8. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Our service is not intended for users under 13 years of age. We do
            not knowingly collect information from children.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>9. Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We will notify users of any material changes to this policy via
            email or platform notification.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2>10. Contact Information</h2>
          <p>For privacy-related inquiries:</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Email: privacy@anonymoussupport.com</li>
            <li>Form: <a href="/contact">Contact Form</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
